#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts a new game. If a game is currently played clears the field and sets "
"the level to 1."
msgstr ""
"नूतनं क्रीडां आरभते। यदि सम्प्रति कश्चन क्रीडा क्रीड्यते तर्हि क्षेत्रं स्वच्छं करोति तथा च स्तरं "
"१ इति सेट् करोति ।"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pause Button"
msgstr "विराम बटन"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pause"
msgstr "विराम"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडा</guimenu> <guimenuitem>विरामं कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pauses or resumes the current game."
msgstr "वर्तमानक्रीडां विरामयति वा पुनः आरभते वा।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menu Items"
msgstr "मेनू-वस्तूनि"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "गेम मेनू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>नव</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game."
msgstr "नूतनं क्रीडां आरभते।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>End Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>खेलसमाप्ति</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ends the current game."
msgstr "वर्तमानक्रीडां समाप्तं करोति।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>P</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>P</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>विरामं कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pauses or resumes the game."
msgstr "क्रीडां विरामयति पुनः आरभते वा।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>उच्चाङ्कान् दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a dialog that displays different high score tables."
msgstr "एकं संवादं उद्घाटयति यत् भिन्नानि उच्चाङ्कसारणीनि प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>निवृत्तं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Quit</action> and close &kbounce;. If a game is currently played, "
"it's status is lost."
msgstr ""
"<action>Quit</action> तथा &kbounce;. यदि सम्प्रति कश्चन क्रीडा क्रीड्यते तर्हि तस्य "
"स्थितिः नष्टा भवति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ध्वनयः वादयन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked, &kbounce; game sounds are played."
msgstr "यदि परीक्षितं तर्हि &kbounce; क्रीडाध्वनयः वाद्यन्ते।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guisubmenu>कठिनता</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a game difficulty. On higher difficulty levels the walls are build "
"slower while balls move faster. That makes it harder to fence an area in the "
"board."
msgstr ""
"एकं क्रीडा कठिनतां चिनुत। उच्चतरकठिनतास्तरयोः भित्तिः मन्दतरं निर्मितं भवति, कन्दुकाः तु "
"द्रुततरं गच्छन्ति । तस्मात् फलकस्य क्षेत्रस्य वेष्टनं कठिनं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kbounce; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"अतिरिक्तरूपेण &kbounce; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा "
"<guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /"
"ulink> तथा च &kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "बहुधा पृष्टाः प्रश्नाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "अहम् अस्य क्रीडायाः स्वरूपं परिवर्तयितुम् इच्छामि। अहं शक्नोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &kbounce; visual theme you can use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kbounce;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"आम्‌। परिवर्तनार्थं &kbounce; दृश्यविषयं भवन्तः मेनूपट्टिकायां "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु &kbounce;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "मया त्रुटिः कृता। अहं पूर्ववत् कर्तुं शक्नोमि वा ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbounce; does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "&kbounce; <quote>Undo</quote> इति विशेषता नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "एतत् क्रीडां कर्तुं कीबोर्डस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोमि वा?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kbounce; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "न &kbounce; कीबोर्डस्य उपयोगेन वादयितुं न शक्यते।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"इदानीं मया क्रीडां त्यक्तव्या, परन्तु अहम् अद्यापि न समाप्तः। अहं मम प्रगतिम् रक्षितुं शक्नोमि "
"वा ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbounce; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kbounce; अस्मिन् क्षणे <quote>रक्षतु</quote> इति विशेषता नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "खेल विन्यास"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kbounce; configuration dialog allows you to select visual themes for "
"&kbounce;."
msgstr "इति &kbounce; विन्याससंवादः &kbounce; कृते दृश्यविषयान् चयनं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"नूतनं विषयं चयनं कर्तुं केवलं चयनसूचिकातः विषयं चिनोतु । सूचीस्थं प्रत्येकं द्रव्यं विषयनामस्य "
"अवशिष्टं लघु पूर्वावलोकनं दर्शयति । तत्क्षणमेव चयनं प्रयुक्तं भवति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select random background pictures from a user defined folder with "
"images."
msgstr "भवान् चित्रैः सह उपयोक्तृनिर्धारितपुटतः यादृच्छिकपृष्ठभूमिचित्रं चिन्वितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> button, located at the bottom part of this dialog."
msgstr ""
"एकदा भवान् भवता चयनितविषयेण सन्तुष्टः अभवत् तदा भवान् <guibutton>OK</guibutton> इति "
"बटन् नुदतु, यत् अस्य संवादस्य अधः भागे स्थितम् अस्ति ।"

